The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 Smoker MP

 New Delhi, Aug. 30 (PTI): A Samajwadi Party member today told the Lok Sabha that he was a chain smoker but was still healthy.

 I am a chain smoker.... I smoke bidi, cigarette, but am healthy, Shyam Chandra Gupt said as the House discussed amendments to a law on advertisements and trade of tobacco and tobacco products.

 His comments drew a strong response from the RJDs Ram Kripal Yadav, who said: He is, in fact, inviting people come and chew tobacco, have ganja. Are you a bidi-maker?




